gh it has not been designated as a trade secret.\r\n\r\n<em>End User</em> – person that acquires Products within the scope of its usual business operations.\r\n\r\n<em>person – </em>any person, including legal entity irrespective of its legal form (joint venture company, limited liability company, partnership and so forth).\r\n\r\n<em>Price List</em> – Product prices made available by Clusterpoint.\r\n<h2>Subject of the Agreement</h2>\r\nPursuant to this Agreement, Clusterpoint grants to You upon payment non-exclusive, limited rights to use the Program and / or provides Technical Support.\r\n\r\nFor the avoidance of any doubt, sale of Program to You is not the subject of this Agreement and Clusterpoint reserves all rights which are not expressly granted to You by this Agreement.\r\n<h2>Territory</h2>\r\nTerritory with regard to which You have been granted rights to use the Program and in which You can receive Technical Support is set out in the Order Form.<strong> </strong>\r\n<h2>Permitted Use</h2>\r\nIf You have chosen the option “<strong><em>STANDARD</em></strong><em>”</em> in the Order Form, You can install, use, access, display, run and interact with the Program in other ways for the purposes of conducting Your usual business during an unlimited period of time, subject to terms and conditions of this Agreement.\r\n\r\nIf You have chosen the option “<strong><em>APS”</em></strong> in the Order Form, You can install, use, access, display, run and interact with the Program in other ways within the scope of conducting Your usual business for a specific purpose as set forth in the Order Form, during an unlimited period of time and subject to terms and conditions of this Agreement.\r\n\r\nIf You have chosen the option “<strong><em>OEM</em></strong>” in the Order Form, You can install, use, access, display, run and interact with the Program in other ways for the purpose of integrating the Program in Your product and assigning it to an End User as a part of Your product