(430, 125, 'faqs_0_title', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, et pro quando scaevola ?'),
(431, 125, '_faqs_0_title', 'field_56b9debe432c2'),
(432, 125, 'faqs_0_text', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, et pro quando scaevola. Has et recteque philosophia, amet justo dignissim duo id, ne per nihil option sanctus. Per convenire argumentum scriptorem cu, quo quis tincidunt maiestatis ad, ea ius meliore facilis. Maiestatis conclusionemque te mea, ei vel choro incorrupte contentiones, quem nullam accumsan nam at. Nec esse aeterno an, sit in falli recusabo gloriatur, ea pri sale audire aeterno. Mel te invenire conceptam.\r\n\r\nId eam impedit singulis, an mea ferri aliquando, ei nec verear audire expetendis. Est quot insolens in. Exerci constituto sed ad, consul appareat pro ei, his no ullum atomorum neglegentur. Vocent assentior quo an, commodo antiopam ad sed.'),
(433, 125, '_faqs_0_text', 'field_56b9dec5432c3'),
(434, 125, 'faqs', '1'),
(435, 125, '_faqs', 'field_56b9deb3432c1'),
(436, 119, 'faqs_0_title', 'Where and how I can create and manage my databases?'),
(437, 119, '_faqs_0_title', 'field_56b9debe432c2'),
(438, 119, 'faqs_0_text', 'All Clusterpoint Cloud DB databases are created from Cloud DB Management Web Console at <a href="https://cloud.clusterpoint.com">https://cloud.clusterpoint.com</a>. Once they are created data within them can be manipulated either from Web Console or through API.'),
(814, 119, 'faqs_3_text', 'Yes – you can create several users under your account with separate (read/write) access rights to each of your databases and other aspects of your account. To get started with this – click on the <strong>Users</strong> link on top of your Cloud DB Management Web Console.\r\nNote: Some types of users will have to be verified (through e-mail) just like your Cloud account was.'),
(439, 119, '_faqs_0_text', 'field_56b9dec5432c3'),
(440, 119, 'faqs', '8'),
(441, 119, '_faqs', 'field_56b9deb3432c1'),
(442, 126, 'faqs_0_title', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, et pro quando scaevola ?'),
(443, 126, '_faqs_0_title', 'field_56b9debe432c2'),
(444, 126, 'faqs_0_text', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, et pro quando scaevola. Has et recteque philosophia, amet justo dignissim duo id, ne per nihil option sanctus. Per convenire argumentum scriptorem cu, quo quis tincidunt maiestatis ad, ea ius meliore facilis. Maiestatis conclusionemque te mea, ei vel choro incorrupte contentiones, quem nullam accumsan nam at. Nec esse aeterno an, sit in falli recusabo gloriatur, ea pri sale audire aeterno. Mel te invenire conceptam.\r\n\r\nId eam impedit singulis, an mea ferri aliquando, ei nec verear audire expetendis. Est quot insolens in. Exerci constituto sed ad, consul appareat pro ei, his no ullum atomorum neglegentur. Vocent assentior quo an, commodo antiopam ad sed.'),
(445, 126, '_faqs_0_text', 'field_56b9dec5432c3'),
(446, 126, 'faqs_1_title', 'Ei his aeque omnium argumentum ? '),
(447, 126, '_faqs_1_title', 'field_56b9debe432c2'),
(448, 126, 'faqs_1_text', 'Ei his aeque omnium argumentum. Mea at illum iisque, dolorem accommodare disputationi pri ad. Nonumy persecuti cum ei. Has habeo volumus cu, esse semper nostrum vis ex. Atqui equidem pertinacia his ea, mei te graeco inciderint. Causae delicata ei has, ocurreret quaerendum no cum, scripta epicurei incorrupte sit eu.'),
(449, 126, '_faqs_1_text', 'field_56b9dec5432c3'),
(450, 126, 'faqs_2_title', 'Sed omnis adhuc intellegat in, omnes saperet eu cum ?'),
(451, 126, '_faqs_2_title', 'field_56b9debe432c2'),
(452, 126, 'faqs_2_text', 'Sed omnis adhuc intellegat in, omnes saperet eu cum. Est unum tota illum ea. Id vide instructior quo, cu scriptorem deterruisset vis, posse signiferumque id ius. Ne usu tale dico democritum. Mei id menandri constituam.\r\n\r\nQui facer nonumes quaerendum ex, pri ea integre labitur deleniti. Ius percipit detraxit repudiare ea, choro evertitur omittantur eu eum. Est ne errem dicant minimum, animal adolescens te sea. Eu diam unum viderer nam.'),
(453, 126, '_faqs_2_text', 'field_56b9dec5432c3'),
(454, 126, 'faqs', '3'),
(455, 126, '_faqs', 'field_56b9deb3432c1'),
(456, 119, 'faqs_1_title', 'Can I use PHPMyAdmin to manage my Clusterpoint Cloud DB databases?'),
(457, 119, '_faqs_1_title', 'field_56b9debe432c2'),
(458, 119, 'faqs_1_text', 'No. PHPMyAdmin is a popular tool to manage MySQL databases, but within Clusterpoint Cloud we are running a No-SQL Clusterpoint Cloud DB. In Clusterpoint Cloud DB all databases are managed from the Web Console.'),
(813, 119, '_faqs_3_title', 'field_56b9debe432c2'),
(459, 119, '_faqs_1_text', 'field_56b9dec5432c3'),
(460, 119, 'faqs_2_title', 'How to create tables in my database?'),
(461, 119, '_faqs_2_title', 'field_56b9debe432c2'),
(462, 119, 'faqs_2_text', 'Tables within a database is a popular concept for several (often relational) database types. In Clusterpoint Cloud DB we do not use this double structure. Documents (database records) are stored directly within the database. If you want to create another ‘table’ – just create another database under your Cloud account.'),
(812, 119, 'faqs_3_title', 'Is it possible to create additional user under one Cloud account or link accounts?'),
(463, 119, '_faqs_2_text', 'field_56b9dec5432c3'),
