(143, 1, '2016-02-15 12:27:40', '2016-02-15 10:27:40', 'a:10:{s:4:"type";s:4:"file";s:12:"instructions";s:0:"";s:8:"required";i:0;s:17:"conditional_logic";i:0;s:7:"wrapper";a:3:{s:5:"width";s:0:"";s:5:"class";s:0:"";s:2:"id";s:0:"";}s:13:"return_format";s:3:"url";s:7:"library";s:3:"all";s:8:"min_size";s:0:"";s:8:"max_size";s:0:"";s:10:"mime_types";s:0:"";}', 'File', 'file', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'field_56c1a81c0e3cf', '', '', '2016-02-15 12:28:30', '2016-02-15 10:28:30', '', 134, 'https://newwww.clusterpoint.com/wp/?post_type=acf-field&#038;p=143', 0, 'acf-field', '', 0),
(151, 1, '2016-02-15 13:03:36', '2016-02-15 11:03:36', 'With all the talk today of the three V’s of big data – volume, velocity, and variety – few people like to mention the three C’s: just how confusing, complicated, and challenging the big data world has become in the few short years since the buzzword hit the scene.\r\n\r\nEven the definition of big data presents a confusing challenge: data sets too large for conventional tools to store, process, or analyze. Big data are a moving target by definition, as new tools enter the market, confounding any notion of conventional.', '￼The secret to easy, fast, economical big data', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '%ef%bf%bcthe-secret-to-easy-fast-economicalbig-data', '', '', '2016-02-16 09:56:25', '2016-02-16 07:56:25', '', 0, 'https://newwww.clusterpoint.com/wp/?post_type=white_papers&#038;p=151', 3, 'white_papers', '', 0),
(148, 1, '2016-02-15 12:35:03', '2016-02-15 10:35:03', 'Support of the transactions consisting of the set of multiple operations is one of the key features of Clusterpoint database server software. It means that in one transaction it is possible to change multiple documents. Transactions are one or more operations that all must succeed. If one operation fails, all the other operations in transaction fail as well, and the database is reversed to the state before the transaction began.', '￼Transaction mechanism in Clusterpoint database', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '%ef%bf%bctransaction-mechanism-in-clusterpoint-database', '', '', '2016-02-24 10:08:20', '2016-02-24 08:08:20', '', 0, 'https://newwww.clusterpoint.com/wp/?post_type=white_papers&#038;p=148', 5, 'white_papers', '', 0),
(149, 1, '2016-02-15 12:58:12', '2016-02-15 10:58:12', 'Over the last few years, big data has become an increasingly important part of the enterprise landscape.\r\n\r\nBig data is generally defined as a data environment that meets the four criteria of volume, veracity, velocity, and variety. That is, a data environment that features a lot (volume) of different kinds of data including text and video (variety), where reliability (veracity) and speed of analysis (velocity) are paramount.', '￼Why are enterprises betting billions on database as a service?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '%ef%bf%bcwhy-are-enterprises-betting-billions-on-database-as-a-service', '', '', '2016-02-15 13:11:58', '2016-02-15 11:11:58', '', 0, 'https://newwww.clusterpoint.com/wp/?post_type=white_papers&#038;p=149', 4, 'white_papers', '', 0),
(150, 1, '2016-02-15 12:56:28', '2016-02-15 10:56:28', '', 'betting-billions-white-paper', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'betting-billions-white-paper', '', '', '2016-02-15 12:56:28', '2016-02-15 10:56:28', '', 149, 'https://newwww.clusterpoint.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/betting-billions-white-paper.pdf', 0, 'attachment', 'application/pdf', 0);
